---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const trailers = [
  {
    title: "Moana Official Teaser",
    date: "2026",
    description: "The first official teaser for the live action adaptation of Disney's beloved Moana. Get your first look at the stunning real-world recreation of the Pacific Ocean adventure.",
    youtubeId: "QKYFfYLe5rs",
    duration: "2:00"
  },
  {
    title: "Moana | Official Teaser",
    date: "2026",
    description: "The official teaser for Disney's Moana live action remake, bringing the animated classic to life with real actors and breathtaking visual effects.",
    youtubeId: "n7f6hlKsxxo",
    duration: "2:30"
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Moana Live Action Trailers - Watch Official Disney Trailers (2026)"
  description="Watch all official Moana live action trailers and teasers. See the first footage of Disney's 2026 live action remake starring Catherine Laga'aia and Dwayne Johnson."
  keywords="moana live action trailer, moana 2026 teaser, moana official trailer, disney moana trailer, watch moana trailer, moana movie preview"
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>🎬 Moana Trailers</h1>
      <p>Watch all official Disney trailers — Moana (2016) & Moana Live Action (2026)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="trailers-section">
    <div class="container">
      {trailers.map((trailer, index) => (
        <div class={`trailer-card ${index === 0 ? 'featured' : ''}`}>
          <div class="video-container">
            <iframe 
              src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${trailer.youtubeId}`}
              title={trailer.title}
              frameborder="0"
              allow="fullscreen"
              allowfullscreen
              sandbox="allow-top-navigation allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-scripts"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="trailer-info">
            <span class="trailer-date">{trailer.date}</span>
            <h2>{trailer.title}</h2>
            <p>{trailer.description}</p>
            <span class="trailer-duration">Duration: {trailer.duration}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="breakdown-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Trailer Breakdown</h2>
      
      <div class="breakdown-card">
        <h3>What We See in the Trailer</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Stunning Ocean Visuals</strong> - The trailer opens with breathtaking shots of the Pacific Ocean, showcasing the incredible visual effects that bring the animated film's water sequences to life.</li>
          <li><strong>Moana's Island Home</strong> - We get our first look at the island of Motunui, recreated in stunning detail with lush tropical landscapes.</li>
          <li><strong>Character Reveals</strong> - The trailer introduces us to Catherine Laga'aia as Moana and gives us glimpses of Dwayne Johnson as the larger-than-life demigod Maui.</li>
          <li><strong>Iconic Moments</strong> - Several beloved scenes from the animated film are recreated, including the memorable boat sequences and the encounter with the Kakamora.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="breakdown-card">
        <h3>Music & Songs</h3>
        <p>The trailers feature snippets of the iconic songs from the original film, including "How Far I'll Go" and "You're Welcome." The live action version will include both the original songs and new additions to the soundtrack.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Where to Watch Moana Live Action Trailers</h2>
      <p>All official Moana live action trailers are available on this page and on Disney's official YouTube channel. The first teaser trailer was released in March 2026, giving fans their first glimpse of the highly anticipated remake.</p>
      
      <h3>How Many Trailers Will There Be?</h3>
      <p>Following Disney's typical marketing pattern, we can expect approximately 2-3 official trailers plus several TV spots and featurettes before the July 2026 release. The full trailer is expected to drop about 2-3 months before the film's premiere.</p>
      
      <h3>What Songs Are in the Moana Live Action Trailer?</h3>
      <p>The trailers feature instrumental versions of the beloved songs from the original film. The full soundtrack, including both classic songs and new additions, will be released closer to the film's premiere date.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077be 0%, #00d4aa 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .page-header p {
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .trailers-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .trailer-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .trailer-card.featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
  }
  
  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 */
    height: 0;
    background: #000;
  }
  
  .video-container iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }
  
  .trailer-info {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .trailer-date {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .trailer-info h2 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .trailer-info p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .trailer-duration {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--light);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  
  .breakdown-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--light);
  }
  
  .breakdown-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .breakdown-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .breakdown-card h3 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .breakdown-card ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .breakdown-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  
  .breakdown-card li strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }
  
  .breakdown-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .seo-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .seo-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .seo-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .seo-content h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .seo-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
